OL,3,CMan guilty of serious sexual abuse of
OL,4,Cyoung child in Jersey
OL,6,FA 36-year-old man has been found
OL,7,Fguilty of serious sexual abuse against
OL,8,Fa young child.
OL,10,FAaron Roy Forsythe Gardner pleaded not
OL,11,Fguilty to serious sexual offences, but
OL,12,Ffollowing two hours of deliberation, a
OL,13,FJersey jury found Gardner guilty on
OL,14,Fall counts.
OL,16,FThe five-day trial at Jersey's Royal
OL,17,FCourt heard a harrowing account from
OL,18,Fthe child, who the prosecution said
OL,19,Fwas abused by the man over a couple of
OL,20,Fyears.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
