FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1781452086
OL,3,CMan guilty of serious sexual abuse of
OL,4,Cyoung child in Jersey
OL,6,FThe evidence included graphic details
OL,7,Ffrom the child about how and where
OL,8,FGardner had allegedly touched them,
OL,9,Fwhich the child described as "naughty
OL,10,Fthings".
OL,12,FThe jury heard how the child told
OL,13,Ftheir mother that they did not want to
OL,14,Fdo the sexual acts, and that it made
OL,15,Fthem sad.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1781452086
OL,3,CMan guilty of serious sexual abuse of
OL,4,Cyoung child in Jersey
OL,6,FThe court also heard from the child's
OL,7,Fmother, who explained that she became
OL,8,Faware of Gardner's behaviour through
OL,9,Fcomments made by the child during
OL,10,Fpotty training and while getting
OL,11,Fdressed.
OL,13,FDetective Garnier of the States of
OL,14,FJersey Police said in a statement:
OL,15,F"These offences represent a profound
OL,16,Fbetrayal which has had a lasting
OL,17,Fimpact on the victim and their family.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
