OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1781452086
OL,3,CMan guilty of serious sexual abuse of
OL,4,Cyoung child in Jersey
OL,6,F"We would like to commend the victim
OL,7,Ffor the immense courage shown
OL,8,Fthroughout the investigation and court
OL,9,Fproceedings. The bravery and
OL,10,Fresilience demonstrated by such a
OL,11,Fyoung person has been extraordinary.
OL,13,F"We hope today's verdict provides some
OL,14,Fmeasure of reassurance and marks an
OL,15,Fimportant step towards recovery for
OL,16,Fthose affected."
OL,18,FGardner will be remanded in custody
OL,19,Funtil sentencing at a later date.
